			<p class="uddharana">‘
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W001">स्मृतिरूपः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W002">परत्र</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W003">पूर्वदृष्टावभासः</span>’ 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W004">इति</span></p>
			<p class="Vyakhya"> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W005">प्रश्नवाक्यस्थितम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W006">अध्यासम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W007">उद्दिश्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W008">लक्षणम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W009">अभिधीयते</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W010">तत्र</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W011">परत्र</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W012">इत्युक्ते</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W013">अर्थात्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W014">परस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W015">अवभासमानता</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W016">सिद्धा</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W017">तस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W018">विशेषणं</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W019">स्मृतिरूपत्वम्</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W020">स्मर्यते</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W021">इति</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W022">स्मृतिः</span> ; 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W023">असंज्ञायामपि</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W024">अकर्तरि</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W025">कारके</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W026">घञादीनां</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W027">प्रयोगदर्शनात्</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W028">स्मर्यमाणरूपमिव</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W029">रूपम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W030">अस्य</span>, 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W031">न</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W032">पुनः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W033">स्मर्यते</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W034">एव</span> ; 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W035">स्पष्टं</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W036">
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W036_L01">पुरोऽवस्थितत्वा</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W036_L02">वभासनात्</span></span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W037">
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W037_L01">पूर्वदृष्टा</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W037_L02">वभासः</span></span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W038">इति</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W039">उपपत्तिः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W040">स्मृतिरूपत्वे</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W041">न</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W042">हि</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W043">पूर्वम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W044">अदृष्टरजतस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W045">शुक्तिसम्प्रयोगे</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W046">रजतम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W047">अवभासते</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W048">
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W048_L01">यतो</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W048_L02">ऽर्थात्</span></span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W049">तद्विषयस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W050">अवभासस्यापि</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W051">इदमेव</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W052">लक्षणम्</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W053">उक्तं</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W054">भवति</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W055">कथम्</span> ? 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W056">तदुच्यते</span> — 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W057">स्मृतेः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W058">रूपमिव</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W059">रूपमस्य</span>, 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W060">न</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W061">पुनः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W062">स्मृतिरेव</span> ; 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W063">पूर्वप्रमाणविषयविशेषस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W064">तथा</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W065">अनवभासकत्वात्</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W066">कथं</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W067">पुनः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W068">स्मृतिरूपत्वम्</span> ? 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W069">पूर्वप्रमाणद्वारसमुत्थत्वात्</span> । 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W070">न</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W071">हि</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W072">असम्प्रयुक्तावभासिनः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W073">
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W073_L01">पूर्व</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W073_L02">प्रवृत्त</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W073_L03">तद्विषय</span>
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W073_L04">प्रमाणद्वारसमुत्थत्वमन्तरेण</span></span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W074">समुद्भवः</span> 
<span id="PP_C01_P12_W075">सम्भवति</span> ॥ </p>
		</div>
