			<p class="Vyakhya">
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W001">सिद्धैव</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W002">ननु</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W003">ब्रह्मजिज्ञासा</span> ? ‘
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W004">अथातो</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W005">धर्माजिज्ञासे’ति</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W006">
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W006_L01">सकलवेदार्थ</span>
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W006_L02">विचारस्योदितत्वात्</span></span> । 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W007">ब्रह्मज्ञानस्य</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W008">च</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W009">चोदनालक्षणत्वेन</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W010">धर्मस्वरूपत्वात्</span> , 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W011">अतः</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W012">सिद्धैव</span> 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W013">ब्रह्मजिज्ञासापि</span> ॥ 
<span id="PP_C02_P01_W014">अभ्यधिकाशङ्काभावादिति</span> । </p>
